Utterance.UttText: Lars Waller, 42 under Dr Gayler, came in with query sepsis with decreasing level of consciousness on the background of chronic renal failure stage 4, on PD (peritoneal dialysis).
He had septic work up done and with pending results.
He is also febrile at 38.6 degrees and is started on IV abs, and IVF on @ 83mls/hr..
blood cultures was taken and awaiting results.
He is written for IV paracetamol.
He is NBM (nil by mouth) due to decreased LOC (level of consciousness).
His PD regimen needs to be reviewed.
Dr __ will come and review patient later.
